flowchart LR
  A[Camera image] --> B[YOLOP road mask]
  A --> C[YOLOv8-seg object mask]
  B --> D[Semantic mask union]
  C --> D
  E[LiDAR point cloud] --> F[Project points to image plane]
  F --> G{Pixel inside semantic mask?}
  D --> G
  G -->|yes| H[Keep point in Semantic ROI]
  G -->|no| I[Discard point]
